1
00:00:04,730 --> 00:00:06,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="12">Unread Messages</font></font></font>

2
00:00:04,730 --> 00:00:06,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Arial"><font size="14"><font color="#4f4d57"><b>Kukuru and Wagari are fighting near
 the hot springs!</b></font></font></font></font>

3
00:00:05,390 --> 00:00:09,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, Kasubata's dead meat.</font>

4
00:00:09,700 --> 00:00:12,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guess I'd better bail him out again.</font>

5
00:00:12,120 --> 00:00:14,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, it's Urusugawa-chan!</font>

6
00:00:16,700 --> 00:00:18,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hugs time!</font>

7
00:00:18,860 --> 00:00:20,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kusaba?!</i></font>

8
00:00:20,290 --> 00:00:23,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you going to see Kasubata-kun?</font>

9
00:00:23,740 --> 00:00:25,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't let you!</font>

10
00:02:14,640 --> 00:02:16,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Eru Kusaba...</i></font>

11
00:02:18,070 --> 00:02:24,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A self-declared "romantic" 
who's actually a walking minefield.</i></font>

12
00:02:24,830 --> 00:02:27,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She falls head-over-heels
for any guy who catches her eye,</i></font>

13
00:02:27,310 --> 00:02:30,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>then scours the net and uses sock puppets
to find out his likes and dislikes.</i></font>

14
00:02:32,630 --> 00:02:37,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And once she knows everything about him, 
she morphs herself into his ideal woman!</i></font>

15
00:02:37,900 --> 00:02:40,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's currently on look number twelve!</i></font>

16
00:02:44,300 --> 00:02:45,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cyber out.</font>

17
00:02:46,530 --> 00:02:47,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Little Mine Book.</font>

18
00:02:47,610 --> 00:02:48,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#0d0e10">Little <font color="#d10074">Mine <font color="#0d0e10">Book</font></font></font></font></font>

19
00:02:48,730 --> 00:02:54,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}When I step on a mine, I can bring out 
120% of the power of a man I've won over.</i></font>

20
00:02:52,110 --> 00:02:54,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#0d0e10">Mixed <font color="#d10074">Martial <font color="#0d0e10">Artist</font></font></font></font></font>

21
00:02:52,110 --> 00:02:54,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#0d0e10">Futo Ryuno</font></font></font>

22
00:02:57,990 --> 00:03:00,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She hits fast... and hard!</i></font>

23
00:03:00,100 --> 00:03:02,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even guarding with my goo, 
she throws hands like a man!</i></font>

24
00:03:02,620 --> 00:03:07,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>By the way, the moment he returns 
my affection, I lose all interest.</i></font>

25
00:03:07,570 --> 00:03:11,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Maybe I only live 
for the love of the chase.</i></font>

26
00:03:09,670 --> 00:03:11,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an3}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#283214">Lame</font></b></font></font>

27
00:03:11,750 --> 00:03:15,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's just the kind of girl I am!</i></font>

28
00:03:16,260 --> 00:03:21,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Targeting me so I can't get to Kasubata 
sounds like playing decoy for your leader.</font>

29
00:03:21,780 --> 00:03:24,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't think 1-A was into teamwork!</font>

30
00:03:24,100 --> 00:03:26,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you've got it all wrong!</font>

31
00:03:26,450 --> 00:03:30,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wagari-san's just so much stronger, 
Kasubata-kun's guaranteed to lose.</font>

32
00:03:30,590 --> 00:03:31,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which means...</font>

33
00:03:32,660 --> 00:03:35,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kasubata! Speak to me!</font>

34
00:03:35,110 --> 00:03:38,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Urusugawa... You patched me up?</font>

35
00:03:40,220 --> 00:03:44,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then he might totally end up 
falling for you, right?!</font>

36
00:03:44,750 --> 00:03:47,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't let that happen! Not ever!</font>

37
00:03:48,160 --> 00:03:50,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can't you get your brain 
out of the gutter for once?!</font>

38
00:03:51,850 --> 00:03:53,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sticky Love Bomb!</font>

39
00:03:52,340 --> 00:03:54,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>{\an9}<font color="#030403">Sticky <font color="#7600de">Love <font color="#030403">Bomb</font></font></font></b></font></font>

40
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:56,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get lost!</font>

41
00:04:06,770 --> 00:04:10,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn. I spent a ton of 
spirit power cushioning my fall.</font>

42
00:04:10,780 --> 00:04:14,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the goo should have her pinned, so...</font>

43
00:04:14,900 --> 00:04:16,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her clothes?</font>

44
00:04:17,190 --> 00:04:24,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font size="16"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#0d0e10">Land <font color="#d10074">Mine <font color="#0d0e10">Connection</font></font></font></font></font></font>

45
00:04:17,230 --> 00:04:21,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}No need to be shy with no boys around!</font>

46
00:04:17,460 --> 00:04:24,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font size="20"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#d10074">Beau<font color="#0d0e10">tician</font></font></font></font></font>

47
00:04:17,460 --> 00:04:24,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="20"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#0d0e10">Shota Ryuha</font></font></font></font>

48
00:04:21,200 --> 00:04:24,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}The camera drones 
can't see us indoors either!</font>

49
00:04:24,030 --> 00:04:25,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides...</font>

50
00:04:27,290 --> 00:04:30,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This <i>is</i> a changing room, isn't it?</font>

51
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:34,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh?</font>

52
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:36,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You sure you want to drop your guard?</font>

53
00:04:40,690 --> 00:04:43,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll beat you down 
even worse than last time</font>

54
00:04:43,510 --> 00:04:46,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so Kasubata-kun will never 
be attracted to you!</font>

55
00:04:46,310 --> 00:04:48,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He isn't anyway!</font>

56
00:04:48,010 --> 00:04:50,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why do you even like him so much?!</font>

57
00:04:52,750 --> 00:04:54,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kasubata-kun...</font>

58
00:04:54,930 --> 00:05:00,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those piercing eyes! That wild masculinity
seething beneath his serious exterior!</font>

59
00:05:00,690 --> 00:05:03,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know, Enishiro-kun's pretty hot, too.</font>

60
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:06,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When they're together, it's just not fair!</font>

61
00:05:06,900 --> 00:05:08,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got rotten taste!</font>

62
00:05:09,710 --> 00:05:11,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't even stick to a single guy!</font>

63
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:18,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is what you looked like 
when you first came to school!</font>

64
00:05:18,300 --> 00:05:21,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you go with the black hair 
to match Kasubata?</font>

65
00:05:21,520 --> 00:05:24,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's not a single part of you 
that's really <i>you!</i></font>

66
00:05:25,730 --> 00:05:27,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you into, Kusaba-san?</font>

67
00:05:27,530 --> 00:05:28,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about you?</font>

68
00:05:28,780 --> 00:05:30,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I like tennis.</font>

69
00:05:30,060 --> 00:05:31,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So do I!</font>

70
00:05:31,770 --> 00:05:34,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love pickled sea cucumber.</font>

71
00:05:34,670 --> 00:05:36,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a grandpa, right?</font>

72
00:05:35,390 --> 00:05:37,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}No, I love sea pineapple!</font>

73
00:05:38,350 --> 00:05:40,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's changing her interests again.</font>

74
00:05:40,830 --> 00:05:42,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's got a new man every day.</font>

75
00:05:42,900 --> 00:05:45,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like changing phone cases.</font>

76
00:05:46,980 --> 00:05:48,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all me!</font>

77
00:05:48,910 --> 00:05:50,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was serious about all of them!</font>

78
00:05:51,110 --> 00:05:54,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just trying to be honest 
to whatever moves my heart!</font>

79
00:05:57,230 --> 00:06:01,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're just a self-repressing 
stalker, Urusugawa-chan!</font>

80
00:06:03,260 --> 00:06:05,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Screw you!</font>

81
00:06:08,180 --> 00:06:10,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Die!</font>

82
00:06:10,670 --> 00:06:12,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Urusugawa-chan...</font>

83
00:06:13,850 --> 00:06:15,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look at this.</font>

84
00:06:15,940 --> 00:06:19,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did it...</font>

85
00:06:19,520 --> 00:06:23,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With your fave, Kureha-kun.</font>

86
00:06:32,330 --> 00:06:33,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font size="16"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#0d0e10">Land <font color="#d10074">Mine <font color="#0d0e10">Connection</font></font></font></font></font></font>

87
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:33,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font size="20"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#d10074">Sumo <font color="#0d0e10">Wrestler</font></font></font></font></font>

88
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:33,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="20"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#0d0e10">Gintakewaka</font></font></font></font>

89
00:06:36,130 --> 00:06:38,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<font size="16"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#0d0e10">Land <font color="#d10074">Mine <font color="#0d0e10">Connection</font></font></font></font></font></font>

90
00:06:36,320 --> 00:06:37,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All a bluff.</i></font>

91
00:06:36,390 --> 00:06:38,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<font size="20"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#d10074">Digital <font color="#0d0e10">Artist 
Ginpei Ishiyama</font></font></font></font></font>

92
00:06:37,820 --> 00:06:41,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Good thing I shopped that up in advance.</i></font>

93
00:06:41,540 --> 00:06:44,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A twofer of physical and mental trauma.</i></font>

94
00:06:44,540 --> 00:06:46,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She'll be totally demoralized now!</i></font>

95
00:06:47,300 --> 00:06:50,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your fave isn't even my type!</font>

96
00:06:54,830 --> 00:06:58,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She thinks she's so great 
just because her family's rich.</font>

97
00:06:58,440 --> 00:06:59,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She sucks.</font>

98
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:01,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She gets whatever she asks for.</font>

99
00:07:01,410 --> 00:07:03,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even the teachers favor her.</font>

100
00:07:03,570 --> 00:07:10,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font face="Arial Black"><font size="36"><font color="#2e3925">Freak</font></font></font></font>

101
00:07:03,570 --> 00:07:10,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Arial"><font size="12"><font color="#46492e">Stay out of school</font></font></font></font>

102
00:07:03,570 --> 00:07:10,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an4}<font face="Arial"><b><font size="18"><font color="#252719">Go back to your ivory tower</font></font></b></font></font>

103
00:07:03,570 --> 00:07:10,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an6}<font face="Arial"><b><font size="20"><font color="#2b392c">Get lost</font></font></b></font></font>

104
00:07:04,460 --> 00:07:07,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This world is shit, 
but at least I have my fave.</i></font>

105
00:07:07,590 --> 00:07:10,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He exists here in the same world.</i></font>

106
00:07:11,100 --> 00:07:13,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That was enough to keep me going.</i></font>

107
00:07:13,450 --> 00:07:18,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kureha-kun's bass playing resonated 
inside me, kept me warm.</i></font>

108
00:07:22,870 --> 00:07:24,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A rope made of goo?!</i></font>

109
00:07:25,500 --> 00:07:27,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How did she recover so quickly?</i></font>

110
00:07:28,150 --> 00:07:30,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew that was a shop job!</font>

111
00:07:31,350 --> 00:07:32,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It took me out for a second,</font>

112
00:07:33,440 --> 00:07:36,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But did you think I wouldn't recognize 
the selfie of him <i>alone</i> in bed</font>

113
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:40,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that he posted to his Insta 
last year on March 2nd at 1:18 AM?!</font>

114
00:07:41,820 --> 00:07:44,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I stared at it over and over...</font>

115
00:07:44,710 --> 00:07:47,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">imagining I was in that bed with him!</font>

116
00:07:47,290 --> 00:07:50,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't underestimate a full-time fangirl!</font>

117
00:07:50,070 --> 00:07:53,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She... She's just like me!</i></font>

118
00:07:53,830 --> 00:07:55,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A total romantic!</i></font>

119
00:07:55,650 --> 00:07:57,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Besides...</i></font>

120
00:08:00,210 --> 00:08:01,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the...</font>

121
00:08:02,450 --> 00:08:07,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All of a sudden, my phone just...</font>

122
00:08:10,110 --> 00:08:12,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did I just do?</font>

123
00:08:12,770 --> 00:08:14,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, there!</font>

124
00:08:14,850 --> 00:08:18,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not safe for a girl 
to be out alone at this hour.</font>

125
00:08:18,670 --> 00:08:19,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I take you home?</font>

126
00:08:19,830 --> 00:08:23,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Buzz off. I don't do 
the sugar daddy thing.</font>

127
00:08:23,220 --> 00:08:25,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">D-D-D... Daddy?!</font>

128
00:08:26,210 --> 00:08:28,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kiyomi Urusugawa-san.</font>

129
00:08:28,910 --> 00:08:30,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That girl went to the hospital earlier.</font>

130
00:08:31,490 --> 00:08:36,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I didn't mean to! She just kept
 mouthing off, so I wished she was dead.</font>

131
00:08:36,450 --> 00:08:39,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-And then... it just...</font>

132
00:08:43,890 --> 00:08:46,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry. I'm sorry.</font>

133
00:08:57,080 --> 00:08:59,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is that?</font>

134
00:08:59,180 --> 00:09:03,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A special power only you and I can see.</font>

135
00:09:03,340 --> 00:09:06,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've unlocked an incredible talent.</font>

136
00:09:08,270 --> 00:09:10,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your classmate is fine.</font>

137
00:09:11,910 --> 00:09:14,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are lots of other kids like you.</font>

138
00:09:14,340 --> 00:09:16,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got cyberkinesis.</font>

139
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:18,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cyberkinesis?</font>

140
00:09:18,640 --> 00:09:21,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you like some training 
to keep it under control?</font>

141
00:09:22,170 --> 00:09:23,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll be with people like you.</font>

142
00:09:24,450 --> 00:09:26,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not just about my fave.</font>

143
00:09:28,090 --> 00:09:30,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't afford to lose!</font>

144
00:09:30,220 --> 00:09:31,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Neither can I!</font>

145
00:09:34,340 --> 00:09:35,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't underestimate me!</font>

146
00:09:35,390 --> 00:09:36,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right back at you!</font>

147
00:09:41,350 --> 00:09:42,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>At this rate...</i></font>

148
00:09:42,860 --> 00:09:43,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll run out of battery!</i></font>

149
00:09:46,590 --> 00:09:48,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Damn it! Any more of this and...</i></font>

150
00:09:48,980 --> 00:09:49,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm going to pass out!</i></font>

151
00:09:50,710 --> 00:09:52,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Cyber off!</i></font>

152
00:10:23,760 --> 00:10:26,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can't move another muscle.</font>

153
00:10:26,660 --> 00:10:28,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me either.</font>

154
00:10:29,230 --> 00:10:31,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Impact"><font color="#3f3c77">M<font color="#6da694">i<font color="#3f3c77">lk</font></font></font></font></font>

155
00:10:31,360 --> 00:10:33,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Impact"><font size="28"><font color="#524caa">M<font color="#6da694">i<font color="#524caa">lk</font></font></font></font></font></font>

156
00:10:33,360 --> 00:10:35,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're good, Kusaba.</font>

157
00:10:35,920 --> 00:10:41,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I take back what I said about you not 
being you. And having a gutter-brain.</font>

158
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:47,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're strong, too. I'm sorry 
I said you were self-repressing.</font>

159
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:55,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also... I've never actually d-done it.</font>

160
00:10:55,880 --> 00:10:57,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font face="Arial"><b><font size="24"><font color="#f4f3f2">Kiyomi Urusugawa
 Eru Kusaba</font></font></b></font></font>

161
00:10:55,980 --> 00:10:57,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font face="Arial"><b><font size="24"><font color="#0c0c0b">Out of the fight</font></font></b></font></font>

162
00:10:58,870 --> 00:11:01,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One win, one draw.</font>

163
00:11:01,260 --> 00:11:03,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Class 1-B is in the lead.</font>

164
00:11:03,820 --> 00:11:07,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Quite a turnabout 
from the last A-B Battle.</font>

165
00:11:07,230 --> 00:11:09,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Class A, under the great Wagari,
 is losing ground.</font>

166
00:11:09,980 --> 00:11:14,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Azaki-sensei, it's too early 
to declare victory.</font>

167
00:11:14,420 --> 00:11:18,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know, Nanzo-sensei, 
this really isn't about me and you.</font>

168
00:11:18,780 --> 00:11:24,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sheesh. And you so used
 to look up to me, too.</font>

169
00:11:24,340 --> 00:11:26,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">P-Principal!</font>

170
00:11:26,620 --> 00:11:30,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm picking up a ghost account 
in the fake Kusatsu, yes!</font>

171
00:11:31,240 --> 00:11:33,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A ghost account?</font>

172
00:11:33,190 --> 00:11:35,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's very faint, but yes!</font>

173
00:11:35,450 --> 00:11:39,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Azaki-sensei, is this another 
ridiculous "surprise" of yours?</font>

174
00:11:39,330 --> 00:11:40,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heck no.</font>

175
00:11:41,110 --> 00:11:43,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Principal, we should investigate.</font>

176
00:11:44,670 --> 00:11:46,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Contact all staff on the premises.</font>

177
00:11:46,890 --> 00:11:48,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Right!</font>

178
00:11:50,150 --> 00:11:55,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It doesn't seem like Nanzo-kun 
or the school set this up.</i></font>

179
00:11:56,050 --> 00:11:57,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's going down over there?</i></font>

180
00:11:58,980 --> 00:12:01,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, it's no use.</font>

181
00:12:01,920 --> 00:12:03,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't stop shaking.</font>

182
00:12:05,760 --> 00:12:08,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suck. I really suck.</font>

183
00:12:08,980 --> 00:12:09,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I...</font>

184
00:12:11,040 --> 00:12:12,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's going on?!</i></font>

185
00:12:18,030 --> 00:12:19,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm not hitting him!</i></font>

186
00:12:20,500 --> 00:12:23,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My flames aren't even grazing him!</i></font>

187
00:12:26,160 --> 00:12:27,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What...</i></font>

188
00:12:28,430 --> 00:12:31,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's he been doing 
these last two weeks?!</i></font>

189
00:12:34,290 --> 00:12:35,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Azaki-sensei.</font>

190
00:12:36,680 --> 00:12:38,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's something I want you to teach me.</font>

191
00:12:42,820 --> 00:12:43,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well?</font>

192
00:12:44,340 --> 00:12:46,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Teach me, Azaki-sensei...</font>

193
00:12:46,620 --> 00:12:49,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">how to use cyberkinesis without a phone!</font>

194
00:12:50,560 --> 00:12:52,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't do that.</font>

195
00:12:53,190 --> 00:12:55,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Surugi does it!</font>

196
00:12:55,980 --> 00:12:58,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I hear you.</font>

197
00:12:58,610 --> 00:12:59,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

198
00:12:59,810 --> 00:13:05,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a bit early, but you might be ready 
to move on to the next stage.</font>

199
00:13:06,030 --> 00:13:07,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The next stage?</font>

200
00:13:09,010 --> 00:13:14,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen up. Standard practice is
 to cyber out directly from your phone.</font>

201
00:13:14,250 --> 00:13:15,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However...</font>

202
00:13:15,900 --> 00:13:18,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can also run spirit power 
<i>through</i> your smartphone</font>

203
00:13:18,300 --> 00:13:20,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and back into your body 
instead of outputting it.</font>

204
00:13:20,880 --> 00:13:22,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-Back into your body?</font>

205
00:13:22,740 --> 00:13:25,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then you can release the output elsewhere.</font>

206
00:13:32,950 --> 00:13:35,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Focus on the flow of spirit power 
in the pit of your stomach.</font>

207
00:13:36,390 --> 00:13:37,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not working...</font>

208
00:13:38,220 --> 00:13:40,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Train hard enough,
and you won't have to hold it.</font>

209
00:13:40,620 --> 00:13:43,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can just have your phone
in contact with your body somewhere.</font>

210
00:13:44,740 --> 00:13:46,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Onipien...</font>

211
00:13:50,930 --> 00:13:53,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">will be able to burn
 more freely than before!</font>

212
00:13:54,420 --> 00:13:57,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I had the laboratory division 
make a smartphone holster for me.</i></font>

213
00:13:57,740 --> 00:14:00,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My spirit power's coursing 
through my body!</i></font>

214
00:14:01,590 --> 00:14:02,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

215
00:14:02,780 --> 00:14:04,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Try harder.</font>

216
00:14:06,570 --> 00:14:09,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Enflame: Eye!</i></font>

217
00:14:07,160 --> 00:14:09,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="30"><b>{\an7}<font color="#0d0d0b">Enflame</font></b></font></font></font>

218
00:14:07,550 --> 00:14:09,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="36"><b>{\an3}<font color="#11cbf9">Eye</font></b></font></font></font>

219
00:14:09,040 --> 00:14:11,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Thank you, Sensei!</i></font>

220
00:14:14,110 --> 00:14:19,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With both hands free, you can integrate
more variety into your attacks, Aori-chan!</font>

221
00:14:20,620 --> 00:14:22,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Thank you, Master!</i></font>

222
00:14:26,040 --> 00:14:27,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why can't I hit him?!</i></font>

223
00:14:30,440 --> 00:14:33,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I can't hit him, then...</i></font>

224
00:14:36,100 --> 00:14:39,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hit me more! More!</i></font>

225
00:14:39,020 --> 00:14:41,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Harder, Enishiro...</i></font>

226
00:14:41,930 --> 00:14:48,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Harder, harder, harder... 
Harder, harder, harder!</i></font>

227
00:14:48,600 --> 00:14:52,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Enishiro, harder!</i></font>

228
00:14:55,110 --> 00:14:57,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Here we go!</i></font>

229
00:14:58,880 --> 00:15:00,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gotcha!</font>

230
00:15:01,040 --> 00:15:03,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Letting you fry me was worth it!</font>

231
00:15:03,500 --> 00:15:05,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's hear you scream!</font>

232
00:15:05,360 --> 00:15:07,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enflame: Shoulder!</font>

233
00:15:06,640 --> 00:15:09,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="30"><b>{\an7}<font color="#0d0d0b">Enflame</font></b></font></font></font>

234
00:15:06,900 --> 00:15:09,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="36"><b>{\an3}<font color="#11cbf9">Shoulder</font></b></font></font></font>

235
00:15:07,130 --> 00:15:09,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nullify Flame Damage!</font>

236
00:15:10,950 --> 00:15:13,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll need a stronger flame 
than that to burn me.</font>

237
00:15:19,560 --> 00:15:22,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, do you give up yet?</font>

238
00:15:23,660 --> 00:15:30,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-That doesn't feel good... at all.</font>

239
00:15:31,580 --> 00:15:34,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're just strong now.</font>

240
00:15:36,540 --> 00:15:38,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It just hurts!</font>

241
00:15:38,790 --> 00:15:41,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It doesn't feel like anything!</font>

242
00:15:41,660 --> 00:15:45,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because it's not infused 
with hatred for me!</font>

243
00:15:47,300 --> 00:15:49,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Love and hate are the same thing.</font>

244
00:15:51,710 --> 00:15:54,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're both strong emotions!</font>

245
00:15:54,350 --> 00:15:56,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="16">{\an8}<b><font color="#3d4243">Dei Surugi  <font color="#abacab">To: <font color="#4fc5ee">atggldq
</font></font></font></b><font color="#484848">HOLY SHIT UR UGLY LOLOLOL GUESS THEY
LET ANYONE BE AN IDOL THESE DAYS
 WHAT ARE YOU A BEHEMOTH</font></font></font></font>

246
00:15:55,210 --> 00:16:00,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So many people hate me online.</font>

247
00:15:56,530 --> 00:15:59,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="16">{\an8}<b><font color="#3d4243">Mayolar <font color="#abacab">To: <font color="#4fc5ee">sO.nWpYzU
</font></font></font></b><font color="#484848">Reported</font></font></font></font>

248
00:15:59,450 --> 00:16:02,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="16">{\an8}<b><font color="#3d4243">Sayaka-chan stan <font color="#abacab">To: <font color="#4fc5ee">sO.nWpYzU
</font></font></font></b><font color="#484848">Who the hell is this guy? 
Pretty sad to get your kicks riling people up online</font></font></font></font>

249
00:16:00,750 --> 00:16:03,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My only regret is that 
I can't see their faces.</font>

250
00:16:02,620 --> 00:16:03,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="16">{\an8}<b><font color="#3d4243">Pavlov-san <font color="#abacab">To: <font color="#4fc5ee">sO.nWpYzU
</font></font></font></b><font color="#484848">Nobody likes you</font></font></font></font>

251
00:16:07,100 --> 00:16:10,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">More... More...</font>

252
00:16:10,630 --> 00:16:11,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, shit!</font>

253
00:16:13,160 --> 00:16:16,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hate me more!</font>

254
00:16:18,830 --> 00:16:20,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're trash.</font>

255
00:16:22,050 --> 00:16:24,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Being in a class with filth like you</font>

256
00:16:25,280 --> 00:16:29,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">goes against every righteous 
fiber of my being.</font>

257
00:16:29,750 --> 00:16:32,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you shouldn't change.</font>

258
00:16:33,070 --> 00:16:35,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're better than someone 
who pretends to be good.</font>

259
00:16:35,220 --> 00:16:37,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, I like you!</font>

260
00:16:41,030 --> 00:16:43,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Getting love and hate at the same time...</i></font>

261
00:16:44,470 --> 00:16:46,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'd never felt that before!</i></font>

262
00:16:46,650 --> 00:16:48,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Such ecstasy!</i></font>

263
00:16:50,160 --> 00:16:53,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">C'mon, Enishiro! You hate me, don't you?!</font>

264
00:16:53,810 --> 00:16:56,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Remember when I torched 
that thing you care about?!</font>

265
00:16:56,750 --> 00:17:01,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hit me with that anger and 
sadness like you did then!</font>

266
00:17:01,310 --> 00:17:03,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Make me come!</font>

267
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:08,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't have time for this, weirdo.</font>

268
00:17:08,380 --> 00:17:11,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Disinterest?</font>

269
00:17:12,320 --> 00:17:14,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's just end this.</font>

270
00:17:14,760 --> 00:17:17,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enflame: Leg!</font>

271
00:17:17,640 --> 00:17:22,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>With my enflamed super-jump, 
I can go fifty meters high!</i></font>

272
00:17:23,690 --> 00:17:26,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll show you one more 
thing you're lacking!</font>

273
00:17:27,270 --> 00:17:28,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A special move!</font>

274
00:17:29,250 --> 00:17:33,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A flame-powered kick with
 the power of gravity behind it...</i></font>

275
00:17:34,150 --> 00:17:38,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Onibi Skill: Flames Falling from Heaven!</font>

276
00:17:49,420 --> 00:17:50,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unbelievable.</font>

277
00:17:51,900 --> 00:17:56,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've made it clear I'm better than him. 
Why does he keep fighting?</font>

278
00:17:56,830 --> 00:17:58,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kukuru!</font>

279
00:17:58,930 --> 00:17:59,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ren!</font>

280
00:18:01,410 --> 00:18:02,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I came to save you!</font>

281
00:18:03,370 --> 00:18:05,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now it's two on one!</font>

282
00:18:16,570 --> 00:18:19,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b><font size="20"><font color="#f4f3f2">Five Minutes Earlier</font></font></b></font></font>

283
00:18:16,940 --> 00:18:19,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Kukuru! Please be safe!</font>

284
00:18:22,840 --> 00:18:26,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a member of Class A 
whose cyberkinesis you don't know?</font>

285
00:18:26,820 --> 00:18:31,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right. He didn't participate 
in the last A-B Battle.</font>

286
00:18:31,840 --> 00:18:34,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He sat out to keep the numbers even.</font>

287
00:18:34,220 --> 00:18:37,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kiri Namekawa. 
Be careful if you run into him.</font>

288
00:18:38,380 --> 00:18:40,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't know what he might do.</font>

289
00:18:42,540 --> 00:18:43,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cyber out...</font>

290
00:18:44,330 --> 00:18:46,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hypnosis App.</font>

291
00:18:50,380 --> 00:18:52,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">May I introduce myself?</font>

292
00:18:52,860 --> 00:18:54,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Kiri Namekawa.</font>

293
00:18:55,000 --> 00:18:59,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My hobbies are watching insects 
and creating fake news.</font>

294
00:18:59,750 --> 00:19:04,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's nothing more fun than 
watching low-information readers</font>

295
00:19:04,170 --> 00:19:05,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">believe lies and do what I want.</font>

296
00:19:06,270 --> 00:19:08,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a lot like watching insects.</font>

297
00:19:09,010 --> 00:19:10,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cyberkinesis: Hypnosis App.</font>

298
00:19:11,370 --> 00:19:17,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If a target looks at my screen, 
I can make them follow my orders.</font>

299
00:19:17,510 --> 00:19:22,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Order: Attack Kukuru Kasubata.</font>

300
00:19:18,800 --> 00:19:21,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Arial"><b><font color="#29241c">Order</font></b></font></font>

301
00:19:19,030 --> 00:19:21,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Arial"><b><font color="#29241c">Attack Kukuru Kasubata</font></b></font></font>

302
00:19:29,320 --> 00:19:32,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I... stabbed Kukuru?</font>

303
00:19:37,290 --> 00:19:39,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">K-Kukuru...</font>

304
00:19:40,670 --> 00:19:44,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does that take them both 
out of the battle now, Wagari?</font>

305
00:19:44,880 --> 00:19:46,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought this might be you.</font>

306
00:19:47,540 --> 00:19:50,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not the conclusion I wanted.</font>

307
00:19:50,040 --> 00:19:53,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really dislike you, Namekawa-kun.</font>

308
00:19:53,420 --> 00:19:57,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I personally like you, Wagari.</font>

309
00:19:58,310 --> 00:20:02,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You smell good. Like the paste 
we used in kindergarten.</font>

310
00:20:02,180 --> 00:20:05,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, let's clean up the rest of them.</font>

311
00:20:05,690 --> 00:20:08,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll find the doll-user in hiding,
 the coward, and...</font>

312
00:20:08,540 --> 00:20:09,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not...</font>

313
00:20:10,360 --> 00:20:13,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not over yet, Wagari.</font>

314
00:20:13,820 --> 00:20:15,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

315
00:20:18,430 --> 00:20:21,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I personally find this irritating.</font>

316
00:20:21,550 --> 00:20:23,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should be controlled.</font>

317
00:20:23,910 --> 00:20:25,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't look, Kukuru!</font>

318
00:20:25,730 --> 00:20:27,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't look at it!</font>

319
00:20:26,830 --> 00:20:29,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Arial"><b><font color="#29241c">Order</font></b></font></font>

320
00:20:27,450 --> 00:20:29,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Order: Dance to death.</font>

321
00:20:27,850 --> 00:20:29,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Arial"><b><font color="#29241c">Dance to death</font></b></font></font>

322
00:20:43,070 --> 00:20:46,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wahoo-hoo-hoo!</font>

323
00:20:46,620 --> 00:20:49,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A sloppy technique 
can be turned back on its user.</font>

324
00:20:50,270 --> 00:20:52,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You caught him off guard with a roar,</font>

325
00:20:52,000 --> 00:20:56,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">forcibly canceling his cyberkinesis, 
which was unstable following output.</font>

326
00:20:58,200 --> 00:21:01,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you still have some life left in you.</font>

327
00:21:01,250 --> 00:21:04,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A slice of true conviction in that 
warped righteousness of yours.</font>

328
00:21:04,150 --> 00:21:07,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I can't cut through to your mind,
this time, I'll sever your limbs</font>

329
00:21:07,810 --> 00:21:10,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and render you physically 
incapable of fighting!</font>

330
00:21:11,770 --> 00:21:14,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't escape with my windows now.</i></font>

331
00:21:14,950 --> 00:21:18,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't die, Kukuru! Just surrender instead!</font>

332
00:21:18,030 --> 00:21:19,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Azaki-sensei, you're watching, right?!</font>

333
00:21:19,930 --> 00:21:21,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Declare him out of the fight!</i></font>

334
00:21:21,930 --> 00:21:22,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Azaki!</font>

335
00:21:23,060 --> 00:21:26,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Azaki-sensei! 
Are you trying to kill your student?</font>

336
00:21:26,220 --> 00:21:27,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Azaki!</font>

337
00:21:27,130 --> 00:21:28,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Azaki-sensei!</font>

338
00:21:28,460 --> 00:21:29,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Shut up!</i></font>

339
00:21:30,140 --> 00:21:32,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You're all pathetic.</i></font>

340
00:21:32,300 --> 00:21:35,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If this fight ends now,
 it's the end of me, too.</font>

341
00:21:37,710 --> 00:21:41,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kukuru... why are you so desperate?</font>

342
00:21:41,530 --> 00:21:45,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't deny I thought 
it was only natural I lost last time.</i></font>

343
00:21:46,450 --> 00:21:48,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm on my last legs in terms of output.</i></font>

344
00:21:49,770 --> 00:21:51,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cyber out.</font>

345
00:21:55,790 --> 00:21:56,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kukuru...</font>

346
00:22:01,060 --> 00:22:02,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that...</font>

